The JSON manifest files in this repository describe how to install the axhub
CLI via Scoop on Windows. The manifests are released for the sole purpose of
enabling installation by users with a valid axhub license.

The axhub binary installed by these manifests is governed by the axhub End
User License Agreement (Proprietary) distributed alongside the binary.

Redistribution or modification of the manifest files is permitted only to the
extent necessary to fork and maintain a private bucket. Any such derivative
must remove all references to "axhub" and "jocodingax" trademarks.

